{"tid":1144762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意外拍下罕見超強正極閃電 直擊窗外壞天氣","createTime":"2019-05-08T09:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T10:53:47.000Z","uid":3090,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0ed684fea1ad3207fade9f289b1e4a42f1b46f","tid":1144762,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPesmko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPesmko.png&h=7163426c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（北美通訊）美國佛羅里達州連日發生午後雷雨，有居民周日拍到連續雷擊實況，數道焰光宛如戰爭片的轟炸場景。美國國家氣象局邁阿密辦公室證實，該名居民拍下的是罕見的「正極閃電（positive lighting）」。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林宜萱<br />\n<br />\n佛州博因頓海灘（Boynton Beach）居民海特（Erica Hite），原本是想拿起手機拍攝窗外風雨，讓家人看看當時天氣有多差，結果正好拍下連環正極閃電的震撼畫面。「正極閃電」出現機率低於5%，發生原因是雲團上部的正電荷大量向下移動，能量比一般閃電強10倍。所幸這幾道正極閃電沒有造成傷亡，只炸毀了垃圾箱。<br />\n<br />\n自上周五起，佛州天氣不穩，洛克斯哈特克黑鎮（Loxahatchee）出現龍捲風，西棕櫚灘周日出現約300次閃電，導致鄉村音樂節活動取消。邁阿密戴德縣降雨最多，博因頓海灘、木星鎮雨量也超過兩吋。<br />\n<br />\n佛州每年6月起常有颶風襲擊，颶風季前即有暴雨，國家氣象局去年將5月15日至10月15日訂為標準雨季。"},{"pid":"ac3ce45b8032c5a1be03dbe739c98f3b6eba42b1","tid":1144762,"uid":73935,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾箱應該上幾世都仆街仔，依世先做垃圾箱同比個咁低出現率嘅雷打中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16445805d3f6a890070f2bbecd0751f3ab32dbe","tid":1144762,"uid":5603,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R87l00WpJN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR87l00WpJN8&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FchYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=1a45d4f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R87l00WpJN8</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2277c6ae2c0cd10a316315c8ec743663d91c764","tid":1144762,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾箱RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd12a40defe7f2900efa4596c5834e62cbf2f343","tid":1144762,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"劉江華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2713e2b13711a2c314498859925889d439c43032","tid":1144762,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"邊個係咁Shazam<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2db0f2a43a3a3f6d90d4071c35b0c6b0370be9f","tid":1144762,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"d4d9b52b1695131109efb997aed3d7080f3da303","tid":1144762,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ac3ce45b8032c5a1be03dbe739c98f3b6eba42b1","tid":1144762,"uid":73935,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾箱應該上幾世都仆街仔，依世先做垃圾箱同比個咁低出現率嘅雷打中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"XXX應該上幾世都仆街仔，依世先做XXX同比個咁低出現率嘅雷打中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47ffb0d5be8c7694739b37d81e1168c54331a2e","tid":1144762,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"真係打到落地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772f176b2d4cfd14944fd8b0981bb160121b44d0","tid":1144762,"uid":4330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"DC又贏"},{"pid":"fdb85a1940dc70c8cc2fc2d97563fdadd4a920dc","tid":1144762,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"畫面震到咁 , 罕見都無鳩用啦"},{"pid":"2e468f810625c87fbc26b38142503f224e3a8445","tid":1144762,"uid":126642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"q